entry.title: Tweezer disinfect
entry.summary:
Vendor: Toronto Lash Supplies
Type:
Price: 14.99

Tweezer Disinfectant 

Purpose of the product: The tweezers can be disinfected so quick and comfortable.
How to Use: Dip the tweezer in a tweezer cleaner and rub it on a sponge to clean it. Take out the tweezer and wipe the remaining debris with a tissue.
Precautions: Use tweezer coated with paint carefully as the tweezer's paint may come off.
Please keep the lid closed after using it.
Use is prohibited outside of the intended use.
Please keep it out of the reach of children.
Capacity: 20ml
